  "title": "OPERATIONS MANAGER",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a dedicated and experienced Operations Manager to oversee the daily operations of our restaurant. The Operations Manager will play a key role in maintaining the highest standards of service, quality, and customer satisfaction. This position requires strong leadership, organizational skills, and a commitment to delivering a superb dining experience</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Manage, motivate, and mentor restaurant staff.</li><li>Optimize restaurant operations by implementing efficient workflows, procedures, and scheduling.</li><li>Ensure a high level of customer satisfaction.</li><li>Collaborate with chefs and culinary teams to develop and update menus, pricing strategies.</li><li>Manage inventory levels, including food, beverages, and supplies.</li><li>Enforce health and safety standards, food safety protocols, and cleanliness guidelines.</li><li>Monitor budget and financial performance.</li><li>Ensure the restaurant's physical appearance is well-maintained.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience as a Operations Manager or in a similar leadership role within the restaurant\n  industry.</li><li>Strong leadership and team management skills.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal abilities.</li><li>Proficiency in restaurant management software and point-of-sale systems.</li></ul>",
